### Admin - list banners
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/banners?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

### Admin - create banner
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/banners
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Summer Drop 2026",
  "subtitle": "Bo suu tap moi",
  "description": "Giam toi da cho item streetwear.",
  "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/demo/image/upload/v1/banner/sample.jpg",
  "isActive": true,
  "sortOrder": 1
}

### Admin - update banner
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admin/banners/{{BANNER_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Summer Drop 2026 Updated",
  "subtitle": "Cap nhat",
  "description": "Noi dung moi",
  "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/demo/image/upload/v1/banner/sample-updated.jpg",
  "isActive": true,
  "sortOrder": 2
}

### Admin - toggle status
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/admin/banners/{{BANNER_ID}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isActive": false
}

### Admin - cloudinary signature
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/banners/cloudinary/sign
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "folder": "banners/homepage"
}

### Public - active banners
GET http://localhost:8080/api/common/banners/active
